{"tid":1086591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水泉澳邨男子圖跳樓　鄰居揭發救回一命","createTime":"2019-04-01T01:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T22:50:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4f32c258249d62e07c8a37952ec54326383f28d0","tid":1086591,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:03:32.000Z","msg":"今日(4月1日)凌晨3時，沙田水泉澳邨欣泉樓一名女子報警，指其樓上單位一名男子危站窗邊，懷疑準備跳樓。警員聯同消防員到場，向該男子規勸，成功令他打消死念。事件中，男子手部受傷，由救護員送院治理，至於尋死原因有待進一步調查。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=83d79ef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190401/mobile/bkn-20190401033951375-0401_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190401%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190401033951375-0401_00822_001.html&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=946d6279\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190401/mobile/bkn-20190401033951375-0401_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dfc09410ab14efc995c4fcd997bedbbaad866a39","tid":1086591,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:17:51.000Z","msg":"危坐通常都唔想死"},{"pid":"c75569e5a8c1aa7c244c1b894b1c373123c4c2cf","tid":1086591,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:18:43.000Z","msg":"有公屋住都仲要死 無撚用"},{"pid":"6425857b989988481a75e1e4d25c4e2cc1b82950","tid":1086591,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:34:48.000Z","msg":"好心做壞事"},{"pid":"cd694ae47429c97425d285ef3846a4933e9d4fd